<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Destiny" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Destiny,</orth> fate: <bibl n="shak. luc 1729" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1729</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 3.3.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. III, 3, 53</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.43" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.151" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 151</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 4.2.91" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 2, 91</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.217" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 4, 217</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 5.1.70" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 1, 70</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.184" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 184</bibl>; cf. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.2.116" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 2, 116</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 3.3.275" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 3, 275</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.6.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 6, 84</bibl>. <cit><quote>by that d. to perform an act,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.252" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 252</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>his d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 1.1.34" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 1, 34</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.57" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 1, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 3.5.17" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. III, 5, 17</bibl>. <cit><quote>my d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.1.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 1, 15</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 3.2.252" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B III, 2, 252</bibl>. Proverbial: <cit><quote>hanging and wiving goes by d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.83" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 9, 83</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>your marriage comes by d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 1.3.66" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 3, 66</bibl></cit>.<lb /><emph>The Destinies</emph> == the Parcae: <bibl n="shak. ven 733" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 733</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ven 733" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 733</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.2.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 2, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.2.111" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 2, 111</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.2.15" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 2, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.137" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 137</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.2.108" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 2, 108</bibl>.
